# 🎉 Implementation Complete: Apple-Inspired Section Headings

## Summary

I've successfully created a professional, reusable **SectionHeading** component based on the Apple design reference you provided. The component implements Apple's precise typography and automatically uses SF Pro Display on Mac while falling back to Inter everywhere else.

## ✨ What You Get

### Core Component
- **`app/components/shared/SectionHeading.tsx`** - Production-ready component
  - ✅ Full TypeScript support
  - ✅ Zero compilation errors
  - ✅ Framer Motion animations
  - ✅ Customizable colors, delays, sizes
  - ✅ Scroll-triggered animations

### Typography (Apple Reference)
```
Font:          Inter → SF Pro Display (Mac) → System
Size:          80px
Weight:        600 (semibold)
Line Height:   84px
Letter Spacing: -1.2px
```

