## 🎨 Visual Design Benefits

### Before
- Multiple heading approaches
- Inconsistent sizing (64px vs 80px)
- Varying letter spacing (-1.28px vs -0.56px vs -0.8px)
- No Mac font optimization
- Different animation strategies

### After
- Unified component
- Consistent 80px sizing
- Precise -1.2px letter spacing (Apple's exact value)
- SF Pro Display on Mac automatically
- Smooth Framer Motion animations
- Single source of truth

