## 💡 Pro Tips

- Mix with existing `SectionHeader` component (they work great together)
- Use `delay` prop to create staggered animation effects across sections
- Set `animate={false}` for any headings that shouldn't animate
- Customize colors with any Tailwind class
- Use on Mac to see SF Pro Display automatically apply!

